{"tid":665829,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抗議將AI運用在武器 Google出現首次集體離職潮","createTime":"2018-05-15T09:58:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T11:51:11.000Z","uid":75969,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"062d2aa67b3a4eda7f2358d934ab54a9a67ec287","tid":665829,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T09:58:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php07rhFa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php07rhFa.jpg&h=0d6bcdf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">目前谷歌有10幾名員工正醞釀集體辭職，表達對谷歌繼續參與軍方Maven項目的抗議，此為谷歌首次大規模辭職潮。（法新社）</span><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕谷歌（Google）4000名多員工3個月前發出內部請願書，呼籲谷歌停止跟軍方合作的Maven項目，現有外媒報導，目前有10幾名員工正醞釀辭職，表達對谷歌繼續參與軍方Maven項目的抗議，這也是谷歌首次出現大規模的辭職潮。<br />\n<br />\n根據《GIZMODO》報導，軍方的Maven項目，是藉由機器學習來識別無人機鏡頭中的車輛和其他物體，加速對無人機鏡頭的分析，從而減輕分析人員的負擔，抗議員工則認為，將AI人工智慧運用在戰爭用無人機有違道德，並認為谷歌此項決策恐將損害用戶信任。<br />\n<br />\n這些辭職的員工表示，谷歌高層對有爭議的商業決策態度已經變得不那麼透明了，並感嘆說，現在谷歌似乎不像以前那樣全心傾聽員工的反對意見。<br />\n<br />\n谷歌也承認使用AI人工智慧用於軍事目的的爭議性，其發言人表示，目前谷歌正草訂關於AI人工智慧的政策與保護措施。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2426442\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2426442&d=fPrERKXOLSGnjnJt4dppo5zN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=248586dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2426442&h=3f10e1bd\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2426442</a>"},{"pid":"8109494008f09066d7e514ef4b98a9c6b04fcc87","tid":665829,"uid":104171,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"062d2aa67b3a4eda7f2358d934ab54a9a67ec287","tid":665829,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T09:58:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php07rhFa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.li